{"tid":741412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普: 英國《太陽報》造假新聞老屈我","createTime":"2018-07-13T15:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T01:36:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"64df84c4676eddaf4f5dc69a703f069804b75da2","tid":741412,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T15:46:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://inews.hket.com/article/2115089/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%20%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%96%87%E7%BF%A0%E7%8F%8A%E8%84%AB%E6%AD%90%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2115089%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9%2520%25E6%25BE%2584%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25BF%25A0%25E7%258F%258A%25E8%2584%25AB%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588&d=aWLXTKQj1tRetMXIM7PMN%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=09f364b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://inews.hket.com/article/2115089/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%20%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%96%87%E7%BF%A0%E7%8F%8A%E8%84%AB%E6%AD%90%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普否認訪問內容 澄清支持文翠珊脫歐方案<br />\n國際 22:18 2018/07/13<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）與英國首相文翠珊（Theresa May）會晤後表示，支持文翠珊政府推動的脫歐方案，<strong>並斥責之前跟他做專訪的英國《太陽報》為假新聞</strong>。文翠珊則指，英國脫歐後有可能與美國達成貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普首先感謝文翠珊的熱情款待，並感謝對方之前支持其增加軍費的建議。他之後談及英國脫歐方案，表示無論文翠珊政府推動哪種脫歐，他也會支持，只需要確定英國可跟美國進行貿易。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》刊登的訪問中，引述特朗普指，文翠珊現時的軟脫歐方案可能抹殺潛在美英貿易協議。特朗普在記者會上斥《太陽報》是假新聞，當中並未刊出他對文翠珊的正面評語。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊亦否定《太陽報》內容，重申英國在脫歐後將可以達成貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普亦重提他對移民的強硬立場，形容移民破壞歐洲文化，帶來恐怖襲擊，造成嚴重負面影響。他又稱，與德國和總理默克爾關係良好，即使政治不正確，但移民確實傷害了德國。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊對此不置可否，僅稱對英國過去接納移民的歷史感自豪，但英國對此應有控制權。"},{"pid":"06d367d41c110a7938f9afa20aabfcb74f250ff7","tid":741412,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f68283d02e37e121e7eda88e05137353e2e59f","tid":741412,"uid":19527,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/103021_740b639741d93ec5079cd6427b1e3deb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F103021_740b639741d93ec5079cd6427b1e3deb.png&h=8c0faa22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n垃圾太陽報不嬲靠假新聞生存"},{"pid":"a2ccc55d10eb3335436478219fc1838596f27065","tid":741412,"uid":17496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:32:06.000Z","msg":"You are fake news"},{"pid":"b3fbc7fb5c1e7fca28d9a28eac1bcd05ba6434e3","tid":741412,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/104034_5a5018d8b24b98bc39e3ae3e6a5a32dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F104034_5a5018d8b24b98bc39e3ae3e6a5a32dc.png&h=bd60d873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國100年前已經充滿fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538cf7615d15affd7d92551f2f311cc3fa016890","tid":741412,"uid":22913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:43:57.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"cef079335e3bee9c3648a0a778bdfab989c7fc6e","tid":741412,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"Sun 同Fox news 咪同一個老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1063bb1e578b97cdf92f5d4abb0a3c90cc982cf4","tid":741412,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:52:51.000Z","msg":"FAKE NEWS"}